    v2 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.84 * v2 + 0.10) + (v0 + 0.36 - tmp + 0.46)))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.04) * (v1 + 0.37 - v2 + 0.93)) + wp.cos(v2))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.91)) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.60 / v2 + 0.68)))
